2026-02-20 20:36:37 - INFO - 716 -{"tools": [{"type": "function", "function": {"name": "tavily_tool", "description": " Tavily tool to search on web  related to the hotel, destination, activities, and other travel-related information.", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"query": {"description": "query", "title": "Query", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["query"], "additionalProperties": false}, "strict": false}}, {"type": "function", "function": {"name": "google_map_tool", "description": " Google Map tool to get distance and duration between source and destination.", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"source": {"description": "source", "title": "Source", "type": "string"}, "destination": {"description": "destination", "title": "Destination", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["source", "destination"], "additionalProperties": false}, "strict": false}}, {"type": "function", "function": {"name": "serper_tool", "description": " Serper tool to search on web  related to the hotel availability and other travel-related information.", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"query": {"description": "query", "title": "Query", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["query"], "additionalProperties": false}, "strict": false}}], "type": "LLMCall", "messages": [{"content": "Validate itinerary using google_map_tool (distances/times), tavily_tool (attractions/hours), serper_tool (hotels/prices). Check if realistic. Say \"APPROVE\" if valid, else suggest fixes.", "role": "system"}, {"role": "user", "name": "user", "content": "I want to two day trip to goa with the budget of 50000. Can you help me plan it?"}, {"role": "user", "name": "Travel_Planner", "content": "## 2\u2011Day Goa Get\u2011away \u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f50,000 (INR) budget  \n*(All prices are approximate for **February\u202f2026** and shown in Indian Rupees. Prices can vary, so book early to lock in the rates.)*\n\n| Category | What\u2019s Included | Approx. Cost (\u20b9) |\n|----------|----------------|-----------------|\n| **Accommodation** (2 nights) | See three hotel tiers below | \u2013 |\n| **Food & Drinks** | Breakfast (incl. hotel), lunch, dinner, snacks, 2\u202f\u00d7\u202fsoft drinks/juice, 1\u202f\u00d7\u202fcocktail/mocktail | \u20b9\u202f4,000\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f7,000 |\n| **Local Transport** | Airport\u2011to\u2011hotel & back (taxi/auto), 2\u2011day scooter rental + fuel, occasional auto\u2011rickshaw | \u20b9\u202f2,500\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f3,500 |\n| **Attractions & Activities** | Beach entry (free), entry fees for forts, museums, water\u2011sport voucher, sunset cruise | \u20b9\u202f3,500\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f5,500 |\n| **Miscellaneous** | Souvenirs, tips, Wi\u2011Fi, emergency buffer | \u20b9\u202f1,000\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f1,500 |\n| **Total (approx.)** | \u2013 | **\u20b9\u202f45,000\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f50,000** |\n\n> **Bottom line:** Even the \u201cluxury\u201d option stays comfortably under the \u20b9\u202f50\u202fk ceiling, leaving a small buffer for extra shopping or a spa treatment.\n\n---\n\n## 1\ufe0f\u20e3 Hotel Options (2\u202fnights)\n\n| Tier | Hotel (Area) | Room Type | Approx. Rate per Night (incl. taxes & breakfast) | Total for 2 Nights | Highlights |\n|------|--------------|-----------|---------------------------------------------------|---------------------|------------|\n| **Budget** | **Casa De Goa \u2013 Guesthouse** (Calangute) | Standard Double | **\u20b9\u202f2,200** | \u20b9\u202f4,400 | Clean rooms, rooftop garden, walking distance to Calangute Beach. |\n| **Mid\u2011range** | **The Flora Residency** (Candolim) | Deluxe Double with sea view | **\u20b9\u202f4,800** | \u20b9\u202f9,600 | Pool, free Wi\u2011Fi, close to Candolim & Baga beaches, good restaurant on\u2011site. |\n| **Luxury** | **Taj Exotica Resort & Spa** (Benaulim) | Ocean\u2011front Deluxe | **\u20b9\u202f12,500** | \u20b9\u202f25,000 | 5\u2011star service, private beach, multiple dining venues, spa & fitness centre. |\n\n*All three hotels include a complimentary breakfast. If you prefer a boutique vibe, **The Park Baga** (mid\u2011range) is another good pick at ~\u20b9\u202f5,200/night.*\n\n---\n\n## 2\ufe0f\u20e3 Transport Details\n\n| Segment | Mode | Approx. Cost |\n|---------|------|--------------|\n| **Airport \u2192 Hotel** (arrival) | Pre\u2011booked taxi/auto (\u2248\u202f10\u202fkm) | \u20b9\u202f800\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f1,200 |\n| **Hotel \u2192 Airport** (departure) | Same as above | \u20b9\u202f800\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f1,200 |\n| **Getting around** | **Scooter rental** (150\u202fkm/day limit) + fuel | \u20b9\u202f350\u202f/\u202fday + \u20b9\u202f150 fuel \u2248 **\u20b9\u202f1,000** total |\n| **Occasional auto\u2011rickshaw** (short hops) | Pay\u2011per\u2011ride | \u20b9\u202f200\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f300 |\n\n*If you prefer not to ride a scooter, a day\u2011pass for **Goa Smart Bus** (\u20b9\u202f300) plus occasional auto\u2011rickshaws will keep you under \u20b9\u202f2,500 total.*\n\n---\n\n## 3\ufe0f\u20e3 Day\u2011by\u2011Day Itinerary  \n\n### **Day\u202f1 \u2013 Arrival, North Goa Highlights**\n\n| Time | Activity | Details / Cost |\n|------|----------|----------------|\n| **08:00** | Arrive at Dabolim Airport | Taxi to hotel (\u20b9\u202f1,000) |\n| **09:30** | Check\u2011in, freshen up | \u2013 |\n| **10:30** | **Calangute Beach** \u2013 stroll, water\u2011sport intro (parasailing) | Parasailing voucher: **\u20b9\u202f1,200** |\n| **12:30** | Lunch at **Fisherman\u2019s Wharf** (Calangute) \u2013 Goan fish thali | **\u20b9\u202f800** |\n| **14:00** | **Fort Aguada** & **Sinquerim Beach** \u2013 historic fort, lighthouse, sea\u2011view photo ops | Entry free, parking **\u20b9\u202f50** |\n| **16:30** | **Baga Beach** \u2013 relax, shop the market stalls | Snacks & drinks **\u20b9\u202f300** |\n| **18:30** | Sunset at **Anjuna Beach** \u2013 watch the famous sunset, optional beach shack dinner | Dinner at **Curlies** \u2013 **\u20b9\u202f1,200** |\n| **20:30** | Return to hotel, night\u2011cap at hotel bar (optional) | Cocktail **\u20b9\u202f500** |\n| **22:00** | Rest / optional early\u2011night walk on the beach | \u2013 |\n\n**Total Day\u202f1 spend (incl. meals, activities, transport):** ~\u20b9\u202f5,200  \n\n---\n\n### **Day\u202f2 \u2013 South Goa & Chill**\n\n| Time | Activity | Details / Cost |\n|------|----------|----------------|\n| **07:30** | Breakfast at hotel (included) | \u2013 |\n| **08:30** | **Old Goa Churches** \u2013 Basilica of Bom\u202fJesus & Se\u202fCathedral (UNESCO sites) | Entry free, donation **\u20b9\u202f50** |\n| **10:30** | **Sahakari Spice Farm** \u2013 guided tour, spice tasting, lunch | **\u20b9\u202f1,200** (incl. lunch) |\n| **13:00** | Head to **Colva Beach** \u2013 relax, optional water\u2011sport (jet\u2011ski) | Jet\u2011ski **\u20b9\u202f1,500** (30\u202fmin) |\n| **15:30** | **Shri Mangueshi Temple** (cultural stop) | Free, modest donation **\u20b9\u202f30** |\n| **17:00** | **Sunset Cruise** on the Mandovi River (live music, snacks) | **\u20b9\u202f1,800** per person |\n| **19:30** | Dinner at **Martin\u2019s Corner** (Betal\u202fVaddo) \u2013 famous Goan crab & pork | **\u20b9\u202f1,200** |\n| **21:30** | Return to hotel, pack, enjoy a night\u2011cap or a walk on the beach | \u2013 |\n| **23:00** | Check\u2011out (if you have a late flight, store luggage at hotel & head to airport) | \u2013 |\n| **23:45** | Taxi to Dabolim Airport | \u20b9\u202f1,000 |\n\n**Total Day\u202f2 spend (incl. meals, activities, transport):** ~\u20b9\u202f6,200  \n\n---\n\n## 4\ufe0f\u20e3 Full Budget Breakdown (example using **mid\u2011range** hotel)\n\n| Item | Cost (\u20b9) |\n|------|----------|\n| **Accommodation** (The Flora Residency) | 9,600 |\n| **Food & Drinks** (Day\u202f1\u202f+\u202fDay\u202f2) | 6,000 |\n| **Local Transport** (airport taxis + scooter + fuel) | 2,500 |\n| **Attractions & Activities** (parasailing, spice\u2011farm, jet\u2011ski, cruise, entry fees) | 5,500 |\n| **Miscellaneous / Souvenirs** | 1,200 |\n| **Grand Total** | **\u20b9\u202f24,800** |\n\n> **Why the total is far below \u20b9\u202f50\u202fk?**  \n> - The mid\u2011range hotel is the most expensive line\u2011item.  \n> - All other categories are deliberately kept modest but still give you a full Goan experience.  \n> - The remaining **\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f25,000** can be used for:  \n>   - Up\u2011grading to a **luxury** stay (adds ~\u20b9\u202f15,400).  \n>   - Adding a **spa treatment** (\u20b9\u202f2,500\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f4,000).  \n>   - More **shopping** at Anjuna flea market or local art galleries.  \n>   - Extending the trip by a night (budget\u2011hotel ~\u20b9\u202f2,200).  \n\n---\n\n## 5\ufe0f\u20e3 Quick Tips & Hacks\n\n| Tip | How it Saves Money / Improves Experience |\n|-----|-------------------------------------------|\n| **Book scooter & hotel together** on platforms like **Goibibo** or **MakeMyTrip** \u2013 you often get a 5\u201110\u202f% bundle discount. |\n| **Eat where locals eat** \u2013 beach shacks (e.g., **Mum\u2019s Kitchen**, **Susegado**) serve authentic Goan fare for \u20b9\u202f300\u2011\u20b9\u202f500 per plate. |\n| **Carry a reusable water bottle** \u2013 refill at hotels or beach kiosks (\u20b9\u202f20 for a large bottle). |\n| **Cash is king** for small vendors & auto\u2011rickshaws; keep \u20b9\u202f2,000\u2011\u20b9\u202f3,000 in small denominations. |\n| **Sun protection** \u2013 sunscreen (\u20b9\u202f250) and a hat will keep you comfortable for long beach hours. |\n| **Travel insurance** \u2013 a basic 2\u2011day policy costs ~\u20b9\u202f300 and gives peace of mind. |\n\n---\n\n## 6\ufe0f\u20e3 Sample Packing List (2\u202fdays)\n\n| Item | Qty |\n|------|-----|\n| Light cotton shirts / tank tops | 2\u20113 |\n| Shorts / comfortable trousers | 2 |\n| Swimsuit / boardshorts | 1\u20112 |\n| Flip\u2011flops + comfortable sandals | 1 each |\n| Sunscreen (SPF\u202f30+) | 1 |\n| Sunglasses & hat | 1 each |\n| Small day\u2011backpack | 1 |\n| Portable charger / power bank | 1 |\n| Basic first\u2011aid (plasters, pain\u2011relief) | \u2013 |\n| Reusable water bottle | 1 |\n\n---\n\n### \ud83c\udf89 Ready to book?\n\n1. **Reserve your hotel** (choose budget/mid/luxury).  \n2. **Pre\u2011book the airport taxi** via **Ola/ Uber** or a local operator.  \n3. **Rent the scooter** online (e.g., **Royal Brothers**, **Goa Bike Rentals**) \u2013 they\u2019ll deliver it to your hotel.  \n4. **Buy activity vouchers** (parasailing, spice\u2011farm, cruise) a day before arrival to lock in prices.  \n\nEnjoy the sun, sea, and spice\u2011laden vibes of Goa! If you need any tweaks\u2014like a different activity mix, a vegetarian\u2011friendly food plan, or a 3\u2011day extension\u2014just let me know. \ud83c\udf34\u2708\ufe0f"}], "response": {"id": "chatcmpl-addfadad-20c3-4e99-97e1-c07545e6ff0e", "choices": [{"finish_reason": "tool_calls", "index": 0, "logprobs": null, "message": {"content": null, "refusal": null, "role": "assistant", "annotations": null, "audio": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "fc_dede63e7-b70a-4dab-849e-07a29763d936", "function": {"arguments": "{\"destination\":\"Casa De Goa, Calangute, Goa\",\"source\":\"Dabolim Airport, Goa\"}", "name": "google_map_tool"}, "type": "function"}], "reasoning": "We need to validate itinerary using google_map_tool, tavily_tool, serper_tool. Check distances/times, attraction hours, hotel prices. Then approve or suggest fixes.\n\nWe need to call tools to verify:\n\n- Distance from Dabolim Airport to Casa De Goa (Calangute) ~ 40 km, time ~1h. Also to Flora Residency (Candolim) similar. Also to Taj Exotica (Benaulim) ~ 30 km.\n\n- Check opening hours of Fort Aguada (open 9am-5pm). Old Goa churches open 9am-5pm. Spice farm hours. Sunset cruise times.\n\n- Hotel rates: verify approximate rates.\n\n- Activity costs: parasailing, jet ski, cruise.\n\nWe'll need to query each.\n\nLet's start with google_map distances."}}], "created": 1771600001, "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "on_demand", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8a618bed98", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 213, "prompt_tokens": 2659, "total_tokens": 2872, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 165, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": null, "queue_time": 0.051734089, "prompt_time": 0.1406479, "completion_time": 0.447744723, "total_time": 0.588392623}, "usage_breakdown": null, "x_groq": {"id": "req_01khxsddd8eb7vyhxtsvp781fg", "seed": 440000125}}, "prompt_tokens": 2659, "completion_tokens": 213, "agent_id": "Travel_Researcher_9c0d9cc4-2e89-41de-9105-53542349de34/9c0d9cc4-2e89-41de-9105-53542349de34"}
